HEADWORD: angrecum
<hw>angrecum</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>any of various
spectacular orchids of the genus <gen>Angraecum</gen> having 2-ranked
dark green leathery leaves and usually nocturnally scented white or
ivory flowers.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

